PrecisOrder which provides for: (a) the leasing to the CITY OF DORVAL, for a term of ten (10) years, of some 156,132.49 square metres of land situate at Montreal International Airport in the City of Dorval, Quebec, which are to be used for the operation of a nine-hole golf course; and (b) the surrender of its current lease (No. 102710).
